# Test Steps

1. Run the backlog generation command using this PRD
2. Confirm one Epic and one Story are created in Jira
3. Assign the Story to an engineer
4. Create a GitHub commit referencing the Jira issue key
5. Confirm the commit appears in the Jira issue activity
6. Verify Jira automatically reflects GitHub activity

